application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Outline application seeking approval of access and layout (with all other matters reserved) for the phased redevelopment of the Rectory Park Estate comprising the demolition of 270 existing residential units and the existing community centre, and the erection of up to a maximum of 425 new residential units and a new community centre together with new and altered roads, refuse and recycling storage, cycle storage, car parking for up to 297 vehicles, public and private amenity space and associated playspace and landscaping
